      description="The pre-trip checklist I use before every Vietnam trip &mdash; packing, logistics, money, and the mistakes I've made so you don't have to."
      bullets={[
        'Pre-departure logistics checklist',
        'Budget planning worksheet (VND & USD)',
        'Transport routing tips for island hopping',
